        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Use <code>time.Now</code> with <code>Unix</code>, <code>UnixMilli</code> or <code>UnixNano</code>
to get elapsed time since the Unix epoch in seconds,
milliseconds or nanoseconds, respectively.</p>

